# Captures are derived artifacts: deterministic, regenerable in seconds, and a
# couple of megabytes of binaries no reviewer can diff. Committing them failed
# once already — a stale set stood as evidence for a UI that was never released,
# and nothing caught it because a changed PNG reads as a byte-count delta.
#
# Regenerate:
#   CAPTURE_DASHBOARD_SCREENSHOTS=1 pnpm --filter @opslane/test-e2e exec vitest run dashboard-screenshots.test.ts
after/*.png
after/manifest.json
after/index.html
